{"word":"ἐθίζω","slug":"ἐθίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐθίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἔθος'><el>ἔθος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to accustom, use</i>, <el>ἐθ. τινὰ ποιεῖν τι</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be</i> or <i>become accustomed</i> or <i>used</i> to do, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b> <p/>"}]}